{
  "text": "At the end of the second major cycle, there were a few hundred thousand people incarnate on Earth. There are over four billion incarnate today. Were the extra, uh the over four billion people who uh are incarnate today, were they uh in the earth uh planes but not incarnate at that time, or did they come in from elsewhere during the last twenty-five thousand year cycle? I am ra. There were three basic divisions of origin of these entities, firstly and primarily, those of the planetary sphere you call Maldek, having become able to take up third density once again, were gradually loosed from self-imposed limitations of form. Secondly, there were those of other third density entrance or neophytes whose vibratory patterns matched the Terran Experiential Nexus. These then filtered in through incarnative processes. Thirdly, in the past approximate two hundred of your years, you have experienced much visiting of the wanderers, it may be noted that all possible opportunities for incarnation are being taken at this time due to your harvesting process and the opportunities which this offers.",
